    "description": "<div>It seems we've been missing updates from One PR lately. <bc-attachment sgid=\"BAh7BkkiC19yYWlscwY6BkVUewdJIglkYXRhBjsAVEkiKWdpZDovL2JjMy9QZXJzb24vMzc5Nzc3Nzk_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIghwdXIGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFQ=--19606959c6a3c98c3fbb380088202c5f0e9e6da6\" content-type=\"application/vnd.basecamp.mention\"><figure>\n  <img data-avatar-for-person-id=\"37977779\" alt=\"Savana\" title=\"Savana, Account Manager at Clixsy\" class=\"avatar\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://bc3-production-assets-cdn.basecamp-static.com/4226914/people/BAhpBLN+QwI=--4f93444a15e54821aa0583160118813b8faa8042/avatar\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\">\n  <figcaption>\n    Savana\n  </figcaption>\n</figure></bc-attachment> mentioned that we probably hit the 12-link threshold. We might need to consider renewing our agreement. What are your thoughts? Should we go ahead with the renewal, or would you prefer to start fresh with SAH and the new vendor? Let me know!<br><br>Cc: <bc-attachment sgid=\"BAh7BkkiC19yYWlscwY6BkVUewdJIglkYXRhBjsAVEkiKWdpZDovL2JjMy9QZXJzb24vMzc5Nzc3Nzk_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIghwdXIGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFQ=--19606959c6a3c98c3fbb380088202c5f0e9e6da6\" content-type=\"application/vnd.basecamp.mention\"><figure>\n  <img data-avatar-for-person-id=\"37977779\" alt=\"Savana\" title=\"Savana, Account Manager at Clixsy\" class=\"avatar\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://bc3-production-assets-cdn.basecamp-static.com/4226914/people/BAhpBLN+QwI=--4f93444a15e54821aa0583160118813b8faa8042/avatar\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\">\n  <figcaption>\n    Savana\n  </figcaption>\n</figure></bc-attachment>&nbsp; <br><br><bc-attachment sgid=\"BAh7BkkiC19yYWlscwY6BkVUewdJIglkYXRhBjsAVEkiLmdpZDovL2JjMy9BdHRhY2htZW50LzgxOTgzMjg1Mj9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiCHB1cgY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVA==--8390121ef13cc152d6b8a2c4d4f40ddd8d49215e\" content-type=\"image/png\" url=\"https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/84f26bb2-135a-11f1-8f8f-0242ac120003/previe